Deployment considerations:

  • Engineered Efficiency Write less, spend less.
  • Non-disruptive everything – deploy once, and upgrade software or hardware in place, with zero impact on performance or application availability.
  • Stay up-to-date, effortlessly eliminate the risk of changes in system environment. Maintain long-term compatibility, IT agility, and peace of mind.
  • Spend more time innovating and less time managing running environment and data for your SQL Server deployment, all underpinned by a customer-first development and support model.
